Class Ingredient

java.lang.Object
com.cb.backend.model.Ingredient
@Entity public class Ingredient extends Object
Entity Ingredient represents a link between a recipe and a product with a specified quantity and measurement unit.

This entity is mapped to the CB_INGREDIENTS table and serves as a association table for the many-to-many relationship between Recipe and Product, enriched with additional attributes such as quantity and unit.

The primary key is a composite key represented by RecipeIngredientKey.

Since:
1.0
Author:
Dmytro Babich
